text: Tarnee Tester (born 22 January 1993) is an Australian rules footballer who plays for Fremantle in the AFL Women's (AFLW). She has previously played for West Coast. ==AFLW career== ===West Coast=== In August 2020, Tester was delisted by West Coast. ===Fremantle=== In August 2020, Tester was signed by Fremantle in the delisted free agency period. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Living people Category:1993 births Category:West Coast Eagles (AFLW) players Category:Australian rules footballers from New South Wales Category:Sportswomen from New South Wales Category:Indigenous Australian players of Australian rules football
